---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Farrier', url: '/for-providers/farrier' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Farrier Services on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your farrier business on the BreederHQ Marketplace. Be seen by breeders and horse owners searching for professional hoof care and shoeing services in their area."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔨</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Farrier Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Trimmers, shoers, corrective farriers, and therapeutic hoof care specialists -
        breeders and horse owners in your area are searching for farrier services on the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-600">
        List Your Farrier Business
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What people search for</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Breeders</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Regular trimming for breeding stock</li>
            <li>Foal and yearling first trims</li>
            <li>Corrective shoeing for young horses</li>
            <li>Broodmare hoof care during pregnancy</li>
            <li>Multi-horse barn schedules</li>
            <li>Show shoeing and performance packages</li>
            <li>Hoof evaluation for pre-purchase exams</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Horse Owners</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Routine trimming and maintenance shoeing</li>
            <li>Corrective and therapeutic farrier work</li>
            <li>Barefoot trimming and natural hoof care</li>
            <li>Laminitis and founder management</li>
            <li>Sport-specific shoeing (dressage, jumping, trail)</li>
            <li>Emergency hoof repair and lost shoes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for farriers</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Guaranteed repeat work</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Hooves grow on a schedule. Every 5-8 weeks, your clients need you again. Breeders with multiple horses mean full-day barn visits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Horse owners search by location and specialty. If you're in their area and do the type of work they need, they find you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Verification builds trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Upload your certifications for a verified badge. Horse owners want a farrier they can trust with their animals' soundness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Profile with specialties, certifications, and travel area</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Coverage area and location-based discovery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Photos of your work and shoeing results</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Flexible pricing display</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Optional verification badge for certifications</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Recommendations from your clients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">$5/mo. No commissions. Cancel anytime.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-200 mb-8">One listing puts your farrier business in front of everyone searching for hoof care on the marketplace.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-emerald-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50">
        List Your Farrier Business
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
